1970 – Bellini: Il pirata – (Cappuccilli, Marti, Baratti; RAI:n Rooman kuoro ja orkesteri; Gavazzeni; EMI CMS5 67121-2)
1972 – Puccini: Turandot – (Pavarotti, Sutherland, Ghiaurov; John Alldis Choir; London Philharmonic Orchestra; Mehta; Decca 414 274-2)
1973 – Rossini: Guillaume Tell – (Bacquier, Gedda, Mesplé, Howell; Ambrosian Opera Chorus; Royal Philharmonic Orchestra; Gardelli; EMI CMS 769951-2)
1973 – Boito: Mefistofele – (Treigle, Domingo, Ligi, Begg; Ambrosian Chorus; London Symphony Orchestra; Rudel; EMI CMS 566 501-2)
1976 – Donizetti: Lucia di Lammermoor – (Carreras, Sardinero, Ramey; Ambrosian Opera Chorus; New Philharmonia; López Cobos; Philips 446 551-2)
1976 – Puccini: Tosca – (Carreras, Wixell, Ramey; Royal Opera House Chorus and Orchestra; Davis; Philips 438 359-2)
1979 – Bellini: Puritaanit – (Kraus, Manuguerra, Hamari; Ambrosian Opera Chorus; Philharmonia Orchestra London; Muti; EMI 769663-2)
